# Ignore everything
*

# Whitelist: project files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!Dockerfile
!MILESTONE1.md
!MILESTONE2.md
!MILESTONE1.pdf
!MILESTONE2.pdf
!eda_article_counts.png
!images/
